As we close out the year, I wanted to share my seven favorite albums of 2024. Why 7? Because seven is Ian’s 🧡favorite number and the number of completion—a perfect way to reflect on the past year’s highlights.

Wishing you and your families the faith to believe, the energy to create, and the love to sustain a peaceful and joyous holiday season. May that faith, love, and joy carry through into the new year and beyond.

-Regina

latestPosts.caption: January 19th is Ian’s Worthday. As we still process his physical absence, we celebrate his presence. We are all in different places on the planet…so is Ian. His spirit is the thread that connects us. Of course orange is your favorite color…Its the fire and the calm. I see you in everything I breath. My absolute favorite thing about myself is being ….Regina the mother of Ian the GodKing. Continue to shine bright,my guiding light. 🧡🧡🧡
Nice Flex @aafca dropping the winners of the awards on #mlkday 🤜🏾🤛🏾Congratulations to all the winners.Thank you AAFCA for recognizing #TheHarderTheyFall
